headline: 1 Wall Street Analyst Thinks Estée Lauder Stock Is Going to $81. Is It a Buy?
summary: Many of Estée Lauder's (NYSE: EL) perfumes and cosmetics make for ideal holiday gifts for folks who appreciate such products.  In the run-up to holiday season, that analyst reiterated her quite bullish stance on the company's prospects.  Last Friday, DA Davidson's Linda Bolton Weiser published a new research note on Estée Lauder.
